sequenceDiagram
  participant U as Unity runtime
  participant GB as GameBootstrapper
  participant P as Planetoid.Awake
  participant DF as DebrisField.Awake
  participant SL as SlingshotLauncher.Awake
  participant FU as first FixedUpdate

  U->>GB: RuntimeInitializeOnLoadMethod<br/>(BeforeSceneLoad)
  GB->>GB: EnhancedTouchSupport.Enable()
  GB-->>U: (editor-only) TouchSimulation.Enable()
  U->>P: Awake — scene object
  U->>DF: Awake — FindAnyObjectByType<Planetoid>()<br/>Configure ParticleSystem + Spawn
  U->>SL: Awake — cache Camera.main
  Note over U,SL: Scene-object Awake order is NOT<br/>guaranteed in general. We code defensively.
  U->>FU: First FixedUpdate (50 Hz)<br/>GravityBody + DebrisField step
